#compdef mdbook-xgettext
# _mdbook-xgettext — extract translatable strings from mdbook to .pot file (google/mdbook-i18n-helpers)
# upstream: https://github.com/google/mdbook-i18n-helpers
# Invoked by mdbook as a renderer; no positional flags.

_mdbook-xgettext() {
    _message 'reads RenderContext JSON on stdin; configured via book.toml [output.xgettext]'
}

_mdbook-xgettext "$@"
